{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"钟声和欢呼","authors":["管桦"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":6,"day":24}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟声和欢呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"管桦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百多年来，祖国的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切忧患，一切压迫和耻辱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都被无数前仆后继的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命者、爱国志士的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水和鲜血洗刷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们已经听到钟声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听到人民的欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这晃动着的群众在欢呼啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万只光辉的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着五星红旗和紫荆花旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在香港升起，在汹涌的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪光的海潮和船舶的上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在蓝色和紫色晨曦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹拂着的海风中飘扬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，我们说世界上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有解放奴隶命运的斗争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是伟大的斗争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：北京市作协）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}